{"tid":767461,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【施丹入魔】22年前原本有機會加盟曼聯","createTime":"2018-08-04T13:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T15:58:04.000Z","uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fa861830ec21d2ef642335eabee2d1ec6c79ec84","tid":767461,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T13:58:40.000Z","msg":"莫連奴喺曼聯地位不穩，英國傳媒甚至話，紅魔高層密謀搵施丹代替寸王領軍，仲提到22年前，其實施丹曾經有機會去奧脫福球場踢波，只不過因為1件事被費格遜否決。 <br />\n<br />\n根據前曼聯主席愛德華嘅自傳所講，施丹成名初期效力波爾多期間，紅魔嘅球探曾經強力推薦佢，就連奧脫福大帝簡東拿都覺得，收購施丹唔會係蝕本生意，可惜當時費爵爺認為，施丹好難同簡東拿共存，所以佢考慮過後，為免影響簡東拿嘅發揮，最後決定放棄收購計劃，最後施丹喺1996年轉會祖雲達斯。"},{"pid":"78b78bf35ea5dbeecf0ecc24dd527d7a71eba581","tid":767461,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T14:00:44.000Z","msg":"防守咁廢點踢曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e61ec04d58d9fbb8e5065fe9678554fd7c4814","tid":767461,"uid":37303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T14:02:56.000Z","msg":"宜家黎都唔遲 老豆"},{"pid":"bcfa2771d701d430548d088553a1e4cc356eee7e","tid":767461,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27e61ec04d58d9fbb8e5065fe9678554fd7c4814","tid":767461,"uid":37303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T14:02:56.000Z","msg":"宜家黎都唔遲 老豆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T14:15:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc129496d19fcfb78be89892e8baba552c1370e","tid":767461,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T14:36:10.000Z","msg":"好睇無黎 一陣變下一個安達臣 華朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"960208e02df93aa1ef83dfec91df53206fd46c07","tid":767461,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T14:38:37.000Z","msg":"獌後防不過不守，而家攻弱守強<br />\n施丹黎到又用自己經驗教到普巴變頂級中場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過前場隻山狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif